(860, 1, '2014-06-06 21:30:55', '2014-06-06 21:30:55', '<h1><span class="bodytext" style="color: #99cc00; font-family: verdana, geneva;"><strong><cite>Know About Us</cite></strong></span></h1>\n\n<hr />\n\n<span style="font-family: verdana, geneva;"><span style="color: #99cc00;"><span style="font-size: 28px;"><span class="bodytext"><strong>Tech Bodhi</strong></span> </span>    <span style="font-size: 20px;"> </span></span><span style="font-size: large;"> ... is a training company focus on Software Development(PHP, Android, IOS and Java),<a href="http://www.techbodhi.co.in/training_services/training/manual-testing/"> Testing</a>, <a href="http://www.techbodhi.co.in/ccna-certification-training/">Networking</a> and Specialized Technology like <a href="http://www.techbodhi.co.in/training_services/training/big-data-hadoop/">Big Data Hadoop</a>,<a href="http://www.techbodhi.co.in/training_services/training/salesforce/">Salesforce CRM, </a><a href="http://www.techbodhi.co.in/training_services/training/automation-testing-selenium/">Automation</a> and  Angular JS. Tech Bodhi has a strong placement cell which enables freshers with <span id="z75l6c4s6_2" class="z75l6c4s6"> Job Opportunities. </span></span></span>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: large; font-family: verdana, geneva;"><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/Uv1z1RD6zGQ2" target="_blank">Tech Bodhi</a> has the sole objective of offering quality education and placement assistance in the IT stream at the most <span style="color: #ff0000;"><strong>affordable prices</strong></span>. With clear and committed focus <a href="https://www.facebook.com/techbodhipune" target="_blank">Tech Bodhi</a> now boasts of hundreds of bright alumni pursuing flourishing careers. We are committed to deliver best talent to industry and flourished the energetic and young Minds</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: large; font-family: verdana, geneva;"><span class="bodytext">We have expertise, a highly experienced faculties and a culture of excellence, we provide our students with intensive training in software which equips them for the challenges of the global economy.</span></span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: large; font-family: verdana, geneva;">Our team has Extensive experience in multiple end to end implementations, maintenance , migration, integration, support &amp; end user training projects.</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: large; font-family: verdana, geneva;"><a href="https://goo.gl/maps/Uv1z1RD6zGQ2" target="_blank"><strong>Tech Bodhi</strong></a> is an IT Consulting and Services Company providing Implementation, Integration, Customization services for Applications Development, Sales Force Platform, Testing Services and Project Management Practice areas</span></p>\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><a href="http://www.techbodhi.co.in/contact-us/inquiry-form/" rel="attachment wp-att-688"><img class="alignnone wp-image-688 size-full" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/cREER.jpg" alt="cREER" width="773" height="267" /></a></p>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\n(function(i,s,o,g,r,a,m){i[\'GoogleAnalyticsObject\']=r;i[r]=i[r]||function(){ (i[r].q=i[r].q||[]).push(arguments)},i[r].l=1*new Date();a=s.createElement(o), m=s.getElementsByTagName(o)[0];a.async=1;a.src=g;m.parentNode.insertBefore(a,m) })(window,document,\'script\',\'//www.google-analytics.com/analytics.js\',\'ga\'); ga(\'create\', \'UA-72559188-1\', \'auto\'); ga(\'send\', \'pageview\');\n// ]]></script>', 'Software Testing Course|PHP|Java|Android|Training|Certification|Institute|Pune', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'software-testing-coursetrainingcertificationautomationinstitutepune', '', '', '2014-06-06 21:30:55', '2014-06-06 21:30:55', '', 0, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=2', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(29, 1, '2014-06-07 07:30:20', '2014-06-07 07:30:20', '<a href="http://www.techbodhi.co.in/contact-us/inquiry-form/" rel="attachment wp-att-627"><img class="alignnone wp-image-627 size-full" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/Placement-Agencies-in-Pune.jpg" alt="Placement-Agencies-in-Pune" width="700" height="300" /></a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><strong>Why We are Different ?</strong></h3>\nOur focus is always to help individuals, or teams, or organizations, be immediately more productive; to achieve more directly as a result of our input; to move out of their comfort zone; to aim higher, do things differently, take risks - more confidently.\n\nWe provide career development skills and knowledge as a "by product" of helping people achieve short term results!\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><strong>Our Core Areas</strong></h3>\nOur core areas of expertise and innovation are Leadership, Teamwork, Technology and Creativity.\n\nIn every Training we deliver, covers the value of Team Work, To work out of comfort zone and build Can Do Attitude\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><strong>Why Our Programs are Different?</strong></h3>\nOur Programs are directly focus on Value for Both - Companies and Students', 'Why Tech Bodhi ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'why-tech-bodhi', '', '', '2014-06-07 07:30:20', '2014-06-07 07:30:20', '', 860, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=29', 0, 'page', '', 0),
