(35, 1, '2014-06-07 08:18:13', '2014-06-07 08:18:13', '<h2>Meet The Team</h2>\n\n<hr />\n\n<strong><a href="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/11110568_988414257843729_3117087685105904809_n.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-619"><img class="alignnone wp-image-619" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/11110568_988414257843729_3117087685105904809_n.jpg" alt="11110568_988414257843729_3117087685105904809_n" width="150" height="150" /></a></strong>\n\n<strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mahendrakamble" target="_blank">Mahendra Kamble</a> </strong>- Mentor\n\nMahendra is a Computer Engineering graduate from MIT Pune. He has 16 years of Successful, Impressive, fast track management career driven by challenges. He is a PMP, Prince2, ITIL; Six Sigma certified IT professional with experience in System Integration, Testing Project Delivery, Project, Process and Quality Management. He has worked with CISCO, ACI Worldwide, Cognizant, Syntel, Zensar, Synecron and Managed complex Project for online banking, Retail Banking, Corporate Banking, Teller Banking and CRM implementation.\n\nHe has handled major clients like:\n\nDevelopment Bank of Singapore, Singapore\n\nInvestec Bank, South Africa\n\nKasikorn Bank, Thailand\n\nIndusind Bank, India\n\nArab Bank, Jordan\n\nSynovus Bank, USA\n\nMoody’s Investment Services, USA\n\n<hr />\n\n<a href="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Naresh-Patole.jpg"><img class="alignnone wp-image-859 size-thumbnail" src="http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/Naresh-Patole-150x150.jpg" alt="Naresh Patole" width="150" height="150" /></a>\n\n<strong><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/naresh-patole-90843513" target="_blank">Naresh Patole</a> </strong>- Mentor\n\nNaresh drives technology strategy, R&amp;D, development and services efforts for Tech Bodhi Solutions. He brings more than 18 years of product development, research, services and strategy experience in BFSI.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nPrior to Tech Bodhi Solutions, Naresh was Principal Technical Architect for the core banking products for DataVision software solutions and front end  banking products in S1 corporation (ACI Worldwide) where he worked on the enterprise solutions for the Banks like DBS Singapore, Kasikorn Bank Thailand, MayBank Malaysia. He was also support manager with S1 Corporation for personal banking product for around 65 financial institutes in United States.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nNaresh earned his master’s degree in Computer Science from Pune University.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\nK. Varsha -  Director, Placement\n\n<hr />\n\nKasturi Sali - Center Head\n\n<hr />\n\nDeepali Wagh - Investor\n\n<hr />\n\nRakesh Mohite - Advisory Board\n\n<hr />\n\nAbhishek Vikash - Advisory Board\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Meet The Team', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'management-team', '', '', '2014-06-07 08:18:13', '2014-06-07 08:18:13', '', 860, 'http://www.techbodhi.co.in/?page_id=35', 0, 'page', '', 0);
